1
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:18,320
Please rest early, miss.

2
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,560
This smoke is poisonous.

3
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,040
Thank you, Lady Consort.

4
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:11,120
Where did this wild sparrow come from?

5
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,920
Dreaming of becoming a phoenix.

6
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,520
Fire!

7
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,360
Help!

8
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:24,240
The fire is too strong!

9
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,640
Quickly, get more water!

10
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,650
Your Majesty, Miss Yulan is still inside.

11
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,520
Your Majesty,

12
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,250
your safety is more important.

13
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,360
Look!

14
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,360
Miss Yulan!

15
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,100
She made it out by herself.

16
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:13,440
Miss Yulan, a fragile young woman,

17
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:15,500
managed to escape the fire unharmed.

18
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,720
It's truly astonishing.

19
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,680
Your Majesty.

20
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,760
I'm fine.

21
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,320
His Majesty has decreed.

22
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:53,720
Miss Yulan is bestowed the title of Lady Lan.

23
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,720
This is your chamber,

24
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,650
Lanyu Pavilion.

25
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,320
Now that you have your own chamber,

26
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:01,520
we can see each other whenever we want.

27
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,800
I never thought my first step into the palace

28
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,330
would be a fight for my life.

29
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,620
This belongs to Lady Li

30
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,760
who dropped it in panic during the fire.

31
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:15,960
What do you plan to do?

32
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,280
Useless!

33
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,600
We agreed she would die in that fire,

34
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:16,080
but instead she performed a phoenix rebirth

35
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,680
that completely captivated His Majesty.

36
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,680
He brought her back to the palace

37
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,120
and even titled her Beauty Lan.

38
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,080
I had planned everything perfectly.

39
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:24,640
Who knows what tricks that wretched girl used

40
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,640
to escape without a scratch.

41
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,160
In a fire,

42
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,280
you just need to wet your clothes with water,

43
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,640
quickly escape from the fire,

44
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:33,770
and you can temporarily avoid injury.

45
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,380
Greetings to Concubine Yushu

46
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,560
and Concubine Lijie.

47
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,080
How dare you!

48
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,480
A mere beauty like you

49
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,760
dares to enter without announcement

50
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,420
and intrude into my chambers.

51
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,720
I've come to present a gift.

52
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,640
My sachet.

53
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,440
You can't possibly think you can use this sachet

54
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,680
to threaten me.

55
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,600
I already said

56
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,560
I came to offer a gift.

57
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,440
The sachet has already been burned.

58
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:22,600
Whether it's a gift or a threat,

59
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:25,000
I have no interest in making deals with you.

60
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,040
The gift is not the sachet,

61
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,960
but rather

62
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:28,840
me.

63
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,680
Have I seen you before?

64
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,080
Jiya

65
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,680
something terrible has happened to my family.

66
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,880
My father has been accused of major corruption

67
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,240
and our family is implicated.

68
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,560
You still come to see me?

69
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,840
Are you trying to get me

70
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:08,760
implicated in this as well?

71
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,050
My father has lived an honest life.

72
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:13,380
He must have been framed by villains.

73
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:18,690
If Your Highness fears being implicated,

74
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:20,440
I will see His Majesty alone

75
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,340
to seek justice for my father.

76
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:28,530
You think you can just see the Emperor?

77
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,760
Back then, I didn't want to enter the palace.

78
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:33,320
But you forced me into the selection of palace ladies

79
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,380
and imprisoned me in the palace cage.

80
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,320
And now that I have power,

81
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:40,100
you still dare to come asking for favors.

82
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:42,600
It was Aunt

83
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:45,440
who was dissatisfied with the marriage my mother arranged for you.

84
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:47,000
It was to secure you a better family

85
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,730
that she sent you to the palace.

86
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,720
What does this have to do with Father?

87
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,360
Shut up.

88
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:57,159
Stop making excuses for your selfishness.

89
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,640
From now on, you are a criminal.

90
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:02,970
There's a world of difference between you and me.

91
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,360
Ji Ruya.

92
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:07,040
Remember your place.

93
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:11,600
Jiya.

94
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,520
Speak.

95
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,520
I am but a common woman.

96
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:34,100
I have no one to rely on in this palace.

97
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,880
I have no intention to compete for favor.

98
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:38,940
That's why I've come seeking Lady Yu Shu's protection.

99
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,679
Ji Ruya is a criminal.

100
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:43,500
How dare she enter the palace if she's alive?

101
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,840
I must be confused.

102
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:57,280
Such a pitiful, lovely face.

103
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:59,840
How could I possibly feel at ease?

104
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,000
Bring me scissors.

105
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:13,320
Why don't I just destroy

106
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:15,000
this face of yours?

107
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:18,160
Then you'll never be able to bewitch His Majesty again.

108
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:20,020
Even if you scarred Yulan's face,

109
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,580
there are so many women in this world.

110
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,560
The Emperor's heart is as vast as the sea.

111
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:26,440
Beautiful women are like spring grass,

112
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,170
wildfire cannot burn them all.

113
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:30,800
How could you possibly eliminate them all?

114
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,960
I believe

115
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,820
if one wishes to secure favor,

116
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:37,220
one should make His Majesty unable to live without you.

117
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,840
In this imperial harem,

118
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:41,400
the Empress is as mild as a chrysanthemum,

119
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:44,320
only Consort Chun and Noble Consort Ning are close rivals.

120
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,850
But her family background far exceeds yours.

121
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,000
If she bears a child first...

122
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:51,000
In the imperial harem,

123
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:54,330
discussing those of higher rank can be punishable by death.

124
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,600
I never intended to enter the palace,

125
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,080
but since I am here,

126
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,640
I naturally must seek

127
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:02,100
protection for my future.

128
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,400
Very good.

129
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,180
You have ambition.

130
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,920
But if you don't seek the Emperor's favor,

131
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,720
what do you want?

